name: Sacrifice
description:
There is chaos in our bones
Demander
To
to be
Free

call

to be free

In the glorious moments of time
Endless
Looking for
To
Free
With pleasure and pain
Never Know
chaos
From our souls
Is
dying
In slow degrees...
